{"tid":1275464,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"我都好想多謝全香港既所有男仔","createTime":"2019-07-01T20:08:17.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-02T11:42:04.000Z","uid":185320,"like":693,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":52,"replies":[{"pid":"3dfca493d7d714a772793822beed94a1b85e5991","tid":1275464,"uid":185320,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-01T20:08:17.000Z","msg":"最近發夢遇到好多好男仔,而且唔知點解,佢地個個都展現威風.<br />\n多謝一直提醒我地要做足安全措施<br />\n多謝比狗個陣時會勇敢保護身邊既同伴<br />\n多謝不理一切長遠同重量都會一齊推鐵馬建立防線做準備.<br />\n多謝即使面對萬千敵軍都不畏恐懼,保持戰意<br />\n多謝係我受傷時候會主動走黎問我洗唔洗生理鹽水或者急救既男仔.<br />\n多謝係狗清場時候,你地依然對身邊左右既人不離不棄,金晴火眼下照顧身邊同行者.<br />\n多謝即使有家庭負擔都願意守護住香港既真男人<br />\n香港既男仔你地絕對都係世界最好！<br />\n能文能武！！"},{"pid":"03f11133ebee48753361bb31a65156dc6fdd570c","tid":1275464,"uid":185320,"like":98,"dislike":3,"score":95,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-01T20:13:00.000Z","msg":"唔好忘記仲有我地爸打啊！！！"},{"pid":"58065661f38c4fd82d6d54601df4dc4b4b98eaa1","tid":1275464,"uid":73804,"like":84,"dislike":4,"score":80,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-01T20:22:56.000Z","msg":"真心覺得香港男仔好犀利<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n能文能武有愛心<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"688daa35dbff800ff50bacb07b0d64cb51514022","tid":1275464,"uid":185320,"like":55,"dislike":2,"score":53,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-01T20:23:01.000Z","msg":"真。港。男。<br />\n勇武智慧兼備！"},{"pid":"6e9eae845430cbee56029e99222728092526485a","tid":1275464,"uid":185320,"like":58,"dislike":1,"score":57,"quote":{"pid":"58065661f38c4fd82d6d54601df4dc4b4b98eaa1","tid":1275464,"uid":73804,"like":84,"dislike":4,"score":80,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-01T20:22:56.000Z","msg":"真心覺得香港男仔好犀利<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n能文能武有愛心<img src=\"/as